00:06:51,600 --> 00:06:54,840
 and say maybe someone who's new to Chicago,

132
00:06:54,840 --> 00:06:56,480
 first time in Chicago,

133
00:06:56,480 --> 00:07:00,640
 and if that someone or your friend is a tourist

134
