00:07:26,080 --> 00:07:28,360
 How do you get to downtown from here, right?

146
00:07:28,360 --> 00:07:30,520
 You can probably, immediately,

147
00:07:30,560 --> 00:07:32,680
 you can answer the question, right?

148
00:07:32,680 --> 00:07:34,480
 Now, if you cannot,

149
00:07:34,480 --> 00:07:36,600
 you probably are deceiving yourself, right?

150
00:07:36,600 --> 00:07:39,320
 You haven't been to Chicago, right?

151
00:07:39,320 --> 00:07:42,000
 Perhaps you are being isolated for so long in COVID

152
00:07:42,000 --> 00:07:44,120
 so you don't know the way, all right?

153
00:07:44,120 --> 00:07:47,120
 Now, it's kind of like that, a puzzle squeak.

