00:08:19,000 --> 00:08:23,360
 and I'm struggling with the meaning,

169
00:08:23,360 --> 00:08:26,840
 the significance of some of the Bible passages, right?

170
00:08:26,840 --> 00:08:29,320
 We're gonna have a Bible study later.

171
00:08:29,320 --> 00:08:32,960
 We are going into the book of Genesis,

172
00:08:32,960 --> 00:08:37,800
 the story of Isaac and Jacob, right?

