00:08:55,880 --> 00:08:59,840
 But the Apostles' Creed is to give us a quick summary

181
00:08:59,840 --> 00:09:04,840
 to tell you and tell me what believing in Christ truly is.

182
00:09:04,840 --> 00:09:07,200
 All right?

183
00:09:07,200 --> 00:09:08,920
 Now I want you to think about it.

184
00:09:08,920 --> 00:09:10,520
 When did you come to faith?

185
00:09:10,520 --> 00:09:12,760
 When did you come to, you know,

186
00:09:12,760 --> 00:09:14,800
 accept Jesus Christ as your Lord and Savior?

187
00:09:14,800 --> 00:09:15,640
 When?

188
00:09:15,640 --> 00:09:18,720
 All right, think about that.

