 How many years ago?

190
00:09:20,520 --> 00:09:21,640
 What day?

191
00:09:21,640 --> 00:09:23,760
 What year, what month, and what day?

192
00:09:23,760 --> 00:09:25,200
 And what circumstances?

193
00:09:25,200 --> 00:09:28,520
 That you come to know Christ.

194
00:09:28,520 --> 00:09:29,600
 All right?

